HEADWORD: jigaboo
<hw>jig"a*boo</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A negro, especially an
African-American; -- an offensive term usually intended as an ethnic
slur.</def> <mark>[vulgar and offensive]</mark> ⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> nigger, spade, coon, nigra.</syn>⟦br⟧
